high_descs: Turn and go to the counter that is to the left of the stove.
Open the cabinet that is above the counter top to the left of the stove. Grab the glass out of the cabinet.
With the glass in hand turn and go to your left to the brown shelf cabinet.
Put the glass on the second shelf in front of the glass that is on the right.
Go to the cabinet that is to the left of the stove.
Open the cabinet that is above the counter to the left of the stove. Grab the glass in the cabinet.
With the glass in hand go to the brown shelf cabinet that is to the left of the counter.
Place the glass to the right of the glass that is on the second shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the glasses away on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the wall, turn right at the wooden shelves and walk to the counter to the left.
Open the cabinet above the green bottle on the counter, pick up the front clear glass and close the door.
Turn around, take a right towards the wall and turn right to face the wooden shelves.
Put the glass on the right side of the second shelf in front of the other glass.
Turn right and hang a left to return to the counter.
Open the cabinet above the green bottle on the counter, pick up the clear glass and close the door.
Turn around, take a right towards the wall and turn right to face the wooden shelves.
Put the glass on the second shelf to the left of the other glasses near the front.
anns.task_desc: Place two glasses on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk across the room and look up to face the cabinet above the wine bottle.
Pick up the glass in the cabinet above the wine bottle.
Step to the left to face the shelves.
Place the glass on the second shelf from the bottom on the right side.
Step to the right and face the cabinet above the wine bottle.
Pick up the glass in the cabinet above the wine bottle.
Step to the left to face the shelves.
Place the glass on the second shelf from the bottom next to the first glass.
anns.task_desc: To move two glasses from the cabinet above the wine bottle to the second shelf from the bottom of the shelves.
